    <div class='pop-up-entry'>
      <div class='pop-up-entry-image-container'>
        <img loading='lazy' src='https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/files/Group_9857.png?v=1683637520' width='450' alt='bride collage image' class='lazyload'>
      </div>
      <div class='pop-up-entry-text-container'>
        <p>If you're a bride who wants to make a statement on your big day, consider a deep side part and soft, carefully styled ringlets. And for those with medium-length hair looking to add some extra volume, seamlessly blend in a set of Ultra Volume hair extensions to complete the look.</p>
        <a href='/pages/bride-lookbook' target='_blank' title='Bride Lookbook Page' class=''>EXPLORE CAMPAIGN</a>
