    <div class='pop-up-entry'>
      <div class='pop-up-entry-image-container'>
        <img loading='lazy' src='https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/files/guest_62d11289-0c98-472b-9990-ebdb56473472.jpg?v=1683812135' width='450' alt='guest collage image' class='lazyload'>
      </div>
      <div class='pop-up-entry-text-container'>
        <p>From gorgeous ponytails to glamorous braids, participating in the celebrations has never looked more promising. Find your perfect look to honour everlasting love in style.</p>
        <a href='/pages/guest-lookbook' title='Guest Lookbook Page' target='_blank' class=''>EXPLORE CAMPAIGN</a>
