    </div>

    <div class='continue-quiz-container'><p onclick='closePopUp()'>Continue Quiz</p></div>
    
  </div>
  <div id='pop-up-mother' class='pop-up-container'>
    <div class='close-container'><p onclick='closePopUp()'><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></p></div>
    
    <h2 class='section-title'>The <em>Mother Of The Bride</em></h2>
    
    <div class='pop-up-entry'>
      <div class='pop-up-entry-image-container'>
        <img loading='lazy' src='https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/files/mother.jpg?v=1683812135' width='450' alt='mother of the bride collage image' class='lazyload'>
      </div>
      <div class='pop-up-entry-text-container'>
        <p>Depth and movement, enhanced by adding a dash of colour with a lightweight set of Classic Full Head extensions. Soft waves and added body bring even finer hair to life for a special day; only the best for the proud mother of the bride.</p>
        <a href='/pages/mother-of-bride-lookbook' title="Bride's Mother Lookbook Page" target='_blank' class=''>EXPLORE CAMPAIGN</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='continue-quiz-container'><p onclick='closePopUp()'>Continue Quiz</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

